Sonatype Nexus Repository
 Wget https://download.sonatype.com/nexus/3/latest-unix.tar.gz
 
 tar -xvf latest-unix.tar.gz
 rename the directory to nexus
 useradd -r -md /opt/nexus nexus
 chown -R nexus.nexus nexus sonatype-work
 cahnge RUN_AS_USER="nexus_user" on nexus.rc
 then run nexus script ./nexus start

Nexus Repository plugin

-- add nexus platform to jenkins
then go to manage jenkins --> configuration find "sonartype Nexus"
add Nexus Repository Manager 3.x Server
give in the necessary data and save


configure nexus repo to add artifacts to nexus Repository 

go to build -- Add Build Step
Add Instance, Repository then click on Add Packages
Group, Artifacts we will find in pom.xml file which is present in github code
Add Maven Artifacts -- Give the file Path
Save and build now
